							<h1 class="entry-title">Gabriela Mistral</h1>

						<p class="post-meta"> por <span class="author vcard"><a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/author/valdepero/" title="Mensajes de Pedro Sevylla" rel="author">Pedro Sevylla</a></span> | <span class="published">Mar 20, 2017</span> | <a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/category/castellano/" rel="category tag">CASTELLANO</a>, <a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/category/castellano/literatura-castellano/ensayo/" rel="category tag">Ensayo</a>, <a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/category/castellano/literatura-castellano/poesia-literatura-castellano/" rel="category tag">poesía</a>, <a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/category/portugues/" rel="category tag">PORTUGUÊS</a>, <a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/category/portugues/traducao/" rel="category tag">Tradução</a> | <span class="comments-number"><a href="http://pedrosevylla.com/gabriela-mistral/#respond">0 Comentarios</a></span></p><img src="http://pedrosevylla.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/1-monumento-en-Vicuña-2.jpg" alt="" class="" width='1080' height='675' />
